{"tid":997731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★好文重溫！香港IT人在政府眼中的社會地位！","createTime":"2019-01-27T11:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T05:23:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3754a506378e92d3121d74e49817d6432df71508","tid":997731,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:45:19.000Z","msg":"IT雖受到社會各階層的歡迎，但以IT為生的職業低層員工卻屬於「賤民」，地位在基層市民之下。雖然有些當紅的IT人，能夠擠身豪們，成為達官貴人的座上客，然而在世人的眼中，他們的人格仍然是低下的，因為IT是供人娛樂的「玩意兒」，IT人就是為人取樂的。<br />\n<br />\n看不起IT人並不僅僅是官員，市民也同樣視IT為最下賤的職業。普通人家如有人去做「IT」，都會被認為是有辱家人，是不肖子孫。凡做「IT」的人要被開除族籍，名字不能上族譜，死後不能葬入宗族墳地。因此，很多人從IT之後，隱姓埋名，幾十年不與家人來往，以免玷辱祖宗。"},{"pid":"c3d49e16309a0252fb4fddcfea31d648e3be514b","tid":997731,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:45:36.000Z","msg":"HK No IT"},{"pid":"28f92ad2dba84af80b58f861ed19919509811762","tid":997731,"uid":182933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9b5df97464bd61c180ce4852bfcdecda4ff648e","tid":997731,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"28f92ad2dba84af80b58f861ed19919509811762","tid":997731,"uid":182933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"&quot;it&quot; is Dog"},{"pid":"d6cd2c6b756dae7140d9ab5c0d4e2fb2c5e0a0c6","tid":997731,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:55:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4166afa0eef62829e983961d1683d0f5d8c77a8e","tid":997731,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57727f727825ca82c7bba472bd87c093240949d5","tid":997731,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T14:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.imgur.com/H2IGwml.gif\" 